PersonalMission.Name: HT-2: Point Blank Shooting
PersonalMission.Description: Even in the most heated battle, your tank can destroy the enemy and survive.
PersonalMission.Hint: The effectiveness of the Sniper mode significantly decreases when the enemy vehicle is getting closer. Sometimes it is better to switch to Arcade aim by pressing Shift or using the mouse wheel.

Primary.Conditions: Destroy 3 vehicles from a distance of 100 m or less
